==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unoriginated
<hw>Un`o*rig"i*na`ted</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Not originated; existing from all eternity.</def> <rj><au>F. W.
Newman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not yet caused to be, or to be made; <as>as,
possible inventions still <ex>unoriginated</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unoriginately</ent>⟦br⟧
